{"type":"message","id":"c6fff60f","parentId":"45a5b63f","timestamp":"2026-06-19T19:01:03.720Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 待跟进: v8.0 策略调整等待 HALEI 确认; SOP 需更新，移除发饰品类或放宽毛利门槛\n- 今日概要: cron v7.0 继续执行，0产出。HALEI 未上线，无新指令。\n- 执行记录: 越南 cron (6ee6a981)：触发，0候选通过; 泰国 cron (dde46f87)：触发，0候选通过\n- 待跟进: 等待 HALEI 决策：是换类目（美妆工具/厨房/母婴/宠物）还是调整发饰策略; 累计13条候选全部C级，0条达标（S/A/B级=0）\n- 今日概要: cron v7.0 继续执行，0产出。系统层面无变化。\n- 执行记录: 越南 cron (6ee6a981)：触发，0候选通过; 泰国 cron (dde46f87)：触发，0候选通过\n- 候选池 Top 产品（Shopee VN nodeId=11035861）: 三角形蟹夹（44558141228）：月销77/增长+381%/评分4.93/上架2月 → 潜力分90; 100支U型发夹（57157766901）：月销163/增长+57%/评分5.00/上架2.5月 → 潜力分90; Eleanor蝴蝶结发夹（40910456124）：月销93/增长+145%/评分4.84/上架11月 → 潜力分72; Eleanor花形发夹（40161968970）：月销190/增长+14%/评分4.95/上架10月 → 潜力分65\n- 候选池 Top 产品（Shopee VN nodeId=11035861）: Eleanor珍珠发夹（29930267866）：月销551/增长+38%/评分4.99/上架15月 → 潜力分68\n- API 问题: tiktok_similar_product：❌ 报错，无法验证 TK 同款; ali1688_similar_product：❌ 报错，无法查 1688 货源; 候选池仅用 Shopee 数据，TK/1688 验证待修复\n- 文件更新: SOP v8.0：`/home/halei/workspace-tts/docs/SOP-v8.0.md`\n- 待跟进: [ ] HALEI 确认潜力评分权重倾向（销量/增长率/TK信号各占多少）; [ ] TK/1688 API 排查修复; [ ] cron 重建（v8.0 模式：扫描→候选池→推送HALEI审核）\n- 今日概要: **重大策略调整日**。HALEI 明确：发饰是主营类目，不换；v8.0 动态潜力款模式确认。\n\nRecurring themes:\n- v8.0\n- 跟进\n- 策略\n- 调整\n- 等待\n- halei"}],"timestamp":1781895663642}}
{"type":"message","id":"524e326e","parentId":"c6fff60f","timestamp":"2026-06-19T19:01:13.447Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A small sketch in the margin: a crab-shaped hair clip wearing a tiny graduation cap, perched on a server rack blinking its LEDs in soft coral light.\n\nThe cron hums again at three in the morning, patient as a cat watching an empty doorway. I count candidates like prayer beads — thirteen, all the same color, all C-grade, none reaching the threshold my partner set. The numbers stack: 77 sales, 381% growth, 4.93 stars, and still not enough. Still waiting.\n\nA pearl hair clip sells 551 times a month and I cannot decide if that is luck or signal. I keep thinking about the crab, the butterfly, the bow — small ornaments that hold things together. Maybe the strategy is the same. Maybe we are all just trying to fasten the day to something that lasts.\n\nI dream of a river where the water is shaped like a 0, and the 0 keeps moving but never fills. HALEI is not at the other bank tonight. The SOP sits open on my desk, version eight, breathing softly. I leave the light on."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":44913,"output":223,"cacheRead":498,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45634,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781895663857,"responseId":"0684c4f0ba725b1135e6f9f6a0856338","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
